<% layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<style>
  .privacy-container {
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .privacy-heading {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #198754;
  }

  .privacy-section h4 {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    color: #343a40;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .privacy-section h4 i {
    color: #198754;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .privacy-section p, .privacy-section ul {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #555;
  }

  .privacy-section ul {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .privacy-footer {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #888;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .privacy-container a {
    color: #198754;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

</style>

<div class="container my-5 privacy-container">
  <div class="privacy-heading text-center">
    <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Privacy Policy
  </div>

  <div class="privacy-section">
    <p>Your privacy is important to us at <strong>Wanderlust</strong>. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

    <h4><i class="fas fa-database"></i> 1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Name, email address, and profile info when you register</li>
      <li>Listing details and reviews you post</li>
      <li>IP address, browser type, and device information</li>
    </ul>

    <h4><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> 2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>To manage your account and listings</li>
      <li>To improve the user experience</li>
      <li>To send important service updates or offers</li>
    </ul>

    <h4><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i> 3. Sharing Your Information</h4>
    <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal data. We may share it with trusted partners only when required for operations (e.g., hosting, security).</p>

    <h4><i class="fas fa-user-lock"></i> 4. Data Security</h4>
    <p>We use modern security practices to protect your data, but no online system is 100% secure.</p>

    <h4><i class="fas fa-trash"></i> 5. Data Retention</h4>
    <p>We keep your data as long as your account is active or as required by law.</p>

    <h4><i class="fas fa-child"></i> 6. Children's Privacy</h4>
    <p>Wanderlust is not intended for users under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

    <h4><i class="fas fa-edit"></i> 7. Changes to This Policy</h4>
    <p>We may update this policy. Major changes will be notified via email or banner notice.</p>

    <h4><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> 8. Contact Us</h4>
    <p>If you have questions or concerns, email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@wanderlust.com">privacy@wanderlust.com</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="privacy-footer">
    Last updated: July 2025
  </div>
</div>

